09:22.000 --> 09:23.567
Now, corporate tax avoidance

09:23.567 --> 09:26.266
has a long and infuriatingly
proud history.

09:26.266 --> 09:29.867
In the 1980s, for instance,
a lawyer named John Carroll Jr.

09:29.867 --> 09:33.133
came up with a tactic to move
U.S. companies offshore

09:33.133 --> 09:36.033
to avoid taxes, and his firm
celebrated him with--

09:36.033 --> 09:38.667
