10:05.133 --> 10:08.467
Now, the tax dodge being
celebrated there

10:08.467 --> 10:10.166
involved taking
an American company

10:10.166 --> 10:11.667
and headquartering it
in Panama,

10:11.667 --> 10:13.000
where taxes were lower,

10:13.000 --> 10:15.567
something its creator
called "the Panama Scoot,"

10:15.567 --> 10:17.967
which sounds like
the name of a tiny elf

10:17.967 --> 10:19.200
