10:24.433 --> 10:27.133
And offshore scooting
is actually something

10:27.133 --> 10:29.600
of a common theme
in corporate tax avoidance.

10:29.600 --> 10:31.967
For decades, companies have
hunted for ways to get

10:31.967 --> 10:33.400
